### QUESTION 2: Spring Boot auto-configuration (clean-signal question)
###
### LlamaIndex results to beat:
###   Vector  : clean 2-sentence answer, top-1 score 0.72
###   BM25    : richer answer with @EnableAutoConfiguration, top-1 score 3.63
###   Hybrid  : BEST answer — META-INF path + Kafka example
### =============================================================================

